// alternatives/amcat.astro — "/alternatives/amcat"
// JSON-LD: THREE separate blocks — Article, FAQPage, BreadcrumbList (per SEO §3.6 / §5.3)
// NO aggregateRating — omitted until real G2/Capterra reviews exist (SEO §13 hard rule)
