        "text": "AMCAT's employer interface allows companies to set score filters and access the candidate pool. The core AMCAT test is standardised and not fully customisable per employer. AssessIQ gives companies complete control to build custom, branded assessments — mixing question types, setting their own rubrics, and running the assessment under their own brand without sharing results with other employers."
