          <p class="font-sans text-aiq-md text-aiq-fg-secondary leading-relaxed m-0">
            AMCAT includes invigilation controls for its administered tests. For detailed, current proctoring specifications, check myamcat.com or the employer interface at employer.aspiringminds.com. AssessIQ's proctoring layer includes tab-switch detection, webcam monitoring with anomaly flagging, full-screen enforcement, and a timestamped event log — visible to the company admin alongside candidate scores.
